data.description: GORGEOUS home on large corner lot in Chadwick Farms and highly sought after Northwest ISD! Beautiful 2-story stone and brick home features 5 bedrooms, 4 full baths, game room, study, and more. The dream kitchen boasts granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, tons of cabinets, and more. The backyard offers a fabulous stone patio with Pergola cover and built in grill perfect for entertaining! Wood floors, crown molding, and more!!!
